indexdef: CREATE UNIQUE INDEX history_ticket_detail_pkey ON public.history_ticket_detail USING btree (id, ticket_id, updatetype)
CREATE INDEX history_edit_date_idx ON public.history_ticket_detail USING btree (("Edit Date" AT TIME ZONE report_at_local_time_test()))
CREATE INDEX "history_ticket_detail_ticket_id_FieldName_idx" ON public.history_ticket_detail USING btree (ticket_id, "FieldName")
